4 and 2003", "bbox": [170.0, 547.9, 1102.1, 568.7]}, {"text": "(shares in thousands):", "bbox": [128.3, 572.9, 318.0, 593.7]}, {"text": "2005", "bbox": [876.9, 605.7, 914.4, 624.5]}, {"text": "2004", "bbox": [954.9, 605.7, 992.4, 624.5]}, {"text": "2003", "bbox": [1036.3, 605.7, 1073.9, 624.5]}, {"text": "Incentive shares, beginning of year . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [170.0, 643.7, 842.0, 664.6]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [917.4, 643.7, 924.4, 664.6]}, {"text": "576", "bbox": [966.7, 643.7, 998.0, 664.6]}, {"text": "1,470", "bbox": [1040.3, 643.7, 1087.2, 664.6]}, {"text": "Incentive shares granted . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [170.0, 668.8, 842.0, 689.6]}, {"text": "113", "bbox": [893.1, 668.8, 924.3, 689.6]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [991.1, 668.8, 998.0, 689.6]}, {"text": "204", "bbox": [1056.0, 668.8, 1087.2, 689.6]}, {"text": "Incentive shares vested . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [170.0, 693.8, 842.0, 714.6]}, {"text": "(1)", "bbox": [907.0, 693.8, 931.3, 714.6]}, {"text": "(538)", "bbox": [959.8, 693.8, 1004.9, 714.6]}, {"text": "(1,066)", "bbox": [1033.4, 693.8, 1094.2, 714.6]}, {"text": "Incentive shares forfeited and canceled . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [170.0, 718.8, 842.0, 739.6]}, {"text": "(5)", "bbox": [907.0, 718.8, 931.3, 739.6]}, {"text": "(38)", "bbox": [970.2, 718.8, 1004.9, 739.6]}, {"text": "(32)", "bbox": [1059.5, 718.8, 1094.2, 739.6]}, {"text": "Incentive shares, end of year . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [170.0, 750.0, 842.0, 770.9]}, {"text": "107", "bbox": [893.1, 750.0, 924.3, 770.9]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [991.1, 750.0, 998.0, 770.9]}, {"text": "576", "bbox": [1056.0, 750.0, 1087.2, 770.9]}, {"text": "Weighted average fair value of incentive shares at grant date . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [170.0, 785.5, 842.0, 806.3]}, {"text": "$49.71", "bbox": [867.0, 785.5, 924.3, 806.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [949.4, 785.5, 959.8, 806.3]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [991.1, 785.5, 998.0, 806.3]}, {"text": "$ 24.94", "bbox": [1023.0, 785.5, 1087.2, 806.3]}, {"text": "Employee Stock Purchase Plan", "bbox": [170.0, 839.4, 441.3, 860.2]}, {"text": "Under the Company’s Employee Stock Purchase Plan (“ESPP’’), substantially all employees can elect to", "bbox": [170.0, 868.4, 1092.8, 889.3]}, {"text": "have up to 10% of their annual wages withheld to purchase Quest Diagnostics common stock. The purchase", "bbox": [128.3, 893.4, 1090.9, 914.3]}, {"text": "price of the stock is 85% of the lower of its beginning-of-quarter or end-of-quarter market price. In 2005, the", "bbox": [128.3, 918.5, 1106.1, 939.3]}, {"text": "Company’s ESPP was amended such that effective July 1, 2005, the purchase price of the stock will be 85% of", "bbox": [128.3, 943.5, 1125.8, 964.3]}, {"text": "the market price of the Company’s common stock on the last business day of each calendar month. Under the", "bbox": [128.3, 968.5, 1110.4, 989.3]}, {"text": "ESPP, the maximum number of shares of Quest Diagnostics common stock which may be purchased by eligible", "bbox": [128.3, 993.5, 1124.5, 1014.3]}, {"text": "employees is 8 million. The ESPP will terminate effective December 31, 2006. The Company plans to submit", "bbox": [128.3, 1018.5, 1104.9, 1039.3]}, {"text": "for approval by the shareholders at its 2006 Annual Meeting of Shareholders an extension of the plan.", "bbox": [128.3, 1043.5, 1039.6, 1064.4]}, {"text": "Approximately 409, 460 and 544 thousand shares of common stock were purchased by eligible employees in", "bbox": [128.3, 1068.5, 1096.6, 1089.4]}, {"text": "2005, 2004 and 2003, respectively.", "bbox": [128.3, 1093.5, 434.1, 1114.4]}, {"text": "Defined Contribution Plan", "bbox": [170.0, 1147.5, 400.6, 1168.3]}, {"text": "The Company maintains a qualiﬁed deﬁned contribution plan covering substantially all of its employees,", "bbox": [170.0, 1176.3, 1094.0, 1197.1]}, {"text": "and matches employee contributions up to a maximum of 6%. The Company’s expense for contributions to its", "bbox": [128.3, 1201.3, 1108.6, 1222.1]}, {"text": "deﬁned contribution plan aggregated $64 million, $62 million and $54 million for 2005, 2004 and 2003,", "bbox": [128.3, 1226.3, 1055.3, 1247.2]}, {"text": "respectively.", "bbox": [128.3, 1251.3, 231.8, 1272.2]}, {"text": "Supplemental Deferred Compensation Plan", "bbox": [170.0, 1305.0, 545.3, 1325.9]}, {"text": "The Company’s supplemental deferred compensation plan is an unfunded, non-qualiﬁed plan that provides", "bbox": [170.0, 1333.9, 1106.5, 1354.7]}, {"text": "for certain management and highly compensated employees to defer up to 50% of their eligible compensation in", "bbox": [128.3, 1358.9, 1128.3, 1379.7]}, {"text": "excess of their deﬁned contribution plan limits. In addition, certain members of senior management have an", "bbox": [128.3, 1383.9, 1084.1, 1404.7]}, {"text": "additional opportunity to defer up to 95% of their variable incentive compensation. The compensation deferred", "bbox": [128.3, 1408.9, 1107.9, 1429.7]}, {"text": "under this plan, together with Company matching amounts, are credited with earnings or losses measured by the", "bbox": [128.3, 1433.9, 1126.9, 1454.7]}, {"text": "mirrored rate of return on investments elected by plan participants. Each plan participant is fully vested in all", "bbox": [128.3, 1458.9, 1103.0, 1479.8]}, {"text": "deferred compensation, Company match and earnings credited to their account. Although the Company is", "bbox": [128.3, 1483.9, 1060.8, 1504.8]}, {"text": "currently contributing all participant deferrals and matching amounts to a trust, the funds in the trust, totaling", "bbox": [128.3, 1508.9, 1100.3, 1529.8]}, {"text": "$25.7 million and $20.9 million at December 31, 2005 and 2004, respectively, are general assets of the", "bbox": [128.3, 1534.0, 1046.7, 1554.8]}, {"text": "F-27", "bbox": [608.9, 1584.0, 648.3, 1604.8]}]}